Bug 2047970 - Feed subscriptions should use <published> date instead of <updated>. r=arschmitz

The fix way back only added item-level published as a fallback for feeds that previously had no usable date.

Atom 0.3 spec uses issued/modified (and not published/updated) - fixing that here as well.

Differential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D307496


